This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) as it proposes a new training method for neural networks. The paper also deals with image classification tasks (cs.CV) and discusses the issue of adversarial attacks (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in its theoretical analysis and practical implementation.
